General.Name: Cullinan Metals Corp.
General.Description: Cullinan Metals Corp. operates as a mining and exploration company. It explores for copper and gold assets. It has an option to acquire 100% interest in the Lac Chavigny gold property comprising 14 contiguous claims located in the province of Quebec; and the Borba 2 property comprising three copper projects and one gold project covering an area of 328.5 square kilometers located in the Ossa Morena of Central Southern Portugal. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
General.Address: 885, West Georgia Street, Vancouver, BC, Canada, V6C 3E8
